1. Installed nvm using:
curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Restarted the terminal.

3. Installed Node version 20.16.0 using:
nvm install 20.16.0
nvm use 20.16.0

4. Installed Sass version 3.7.4 using:
npm install sass -v 3.7.4

5. Verified the installation using:
npm list sass

